"Prince Eagle." Mythical bird, the mount of Agni (bringer of fire), eagle demon, associated with the aspect of the Phoenix. Very scholarly study, the equal of Dragon, utilizes all aspects of human, animal, spirit, immortal models.

Reference in [[Google Books/Weapons & Fighting Arts of Indonesia]], p. 42.

